Fun fact: this dude is used to make some really fine comic called "Anak Kos Dodol" which roughly translated means "Stupid Dorm Kids". It's an absolutely normal comic about silly girls living in girl dormitory doing silly things. Jati, however, as you all might expected, got absolutely criticized and harshly condemned by every Indonesian fictional/non-fictional writers for publishing his works contains Mother-Son pedophillia. You can take a wild guess about what they thought when he made "gore" works like this.

The continuation of this comic will be guro. How do I know this? There's a "JLEB" sound effect at the very end of page three times.  It's a sound effect used in Indonesian works for objects that thrusts. It's either a dick or a knife. I'm willing to bet on the latter.
